metadata.name: Lux's Me
metadata.description:
Introducing Another Level NFTs Creator's latest collection, featuring a new character design that takes the goddess Lakshmi, known for her association with love, wealth, and fortune, to a new level. Our innovative approach blends her traditional attire with a casual look sport woman while still maintaining the moo-tae-loo concept by incorporating a Thai talisman into the design. 

Don't miss the chance to mint these NFTs and reserve your seat to limited edition more to come
